                     <interp inst="t18320906-307-person2538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer of Worship-street. -When the summons was heard the Magistrate directed me to take the prisoner - I received the bag and money from Lealter.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-307-person2539">
